### **4. 23_LivePlotSync**  
**Description:**  
Visualizes incoming numerical data with real-time updates on a synced scrolling chart.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# LivePlotSync - Real-Time Data Plotter

LivePlotSync transforms data streams into animated line charts for dashboards or performance monitoring.

## Features
- Matplotlib live chart  
- Smooth scrolling  
- Adjustable refresh speed  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_LivePlotSync.git
cd 23_LivePlotSync
python visualize.py
